The first layer

InteractItemAction(BM):
interact_with: Union[List of options of item like, ArthurBook, TV, MusicBox, Computer, etc item_name]


The second layer
item_name(BM): (dynamically generating this layer, like ArthurBook, TV, MusicBox, Computer)
item_name: Literal[item_name]
action: Union[List of options like reading, writing, playing, etc action_name]


The third layer
action_name(BM): (dynamically generating this layer, like reading, writing, playing, etc action_name)
action_name: Literal[action_name]
parameter: str (whether this one exist depending on how item is being declare item)



Do you know have a better picture of how to construct it?
